Pseudocode:

To check positive or negative number

PROMPT for positive or negative

GET the n for positive result

IF n is greater than zero

DISPLAY “Print positive”

ELSE

DISPLAY “Print negative”

END IF

To check odd or even number

PROMPT for check odd or even number

GET the odd or even number

IF n percent 2 equals zero

DISPLAY

Print “number is even”

ELSE

DISPLAY

Print “number is odd”

END IF
